<p class="ayah 80-12" id="12" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَمَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So whosoever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَآءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">wills</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَكَرَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">may remember it.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>12<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
