<p class="ayah 80-14" id="14" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّرْفُوعَةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Exalted,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّطَهَّرَةِۭ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">purified,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>14<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
