<p class="ayah 80-19" id="19" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">From</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نُّطْفَةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a sperm drop</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَلَقَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He created him,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَقَدَّرَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then He proportioned him,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>19<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
