<p class="ayah 80-24" id="24" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلْيَنظُرِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then let look</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the man</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">at</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">طَعَامِهِۦٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">his food,</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>24<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
